channel.title: Need a Client for
channel.description: Hi, I need a Client that I can use to play my own server. I want to test the server before putting it online, and all the clients I download I can't run because i get an error "Can't Connect - retrying in 5...4...3...2...1...10...9...8..." etc. Please give me a client I can use for my Allstar-Scape server that is offline till I code it. Thank you.
